## Verification Plan
1. **API Testing**: I will use local Python test scripts or Django test client to verify [Message](file:///c:/dev/projects/health_tracker_system/backend/api/models.py#35-47) endpoints can send and receive texts concurrently.
2. **PDF Verification**: I will use the browser dashboard locally (`flutter run -d chrome`) to fetch mock patient data and verify the downloaded PDF file is formatted beautifully.
3. **Chat Sync**: I will deploy to the Mobile phone and the Provider Web app simultaneously to ensure texts sent from Mobile appear on the Dashboard, and vice versa.
